This plugin provides a high-performance, low-latency Advanced Packet Inspection engine for OPNsense,
supporting Stateful and Stateless inspection under Zero Trust principles.

Key Features:
- Inspects individual packets (stateless) and full sessions (stateful).
- Operates in resource-constrained and industrial OT environments (e.g., SCADA, PLC).
- Rule-based evaluation with logging and alerting.
- Zero Trust architecture: every packet is untrusted until verified.
- Fully implemented in Python for performance and flexibility.

